snippets.title: ManagedKafka addAclEntry Sample
snippets.description: Incremental update: Adds an acl entry to an acl. Creates the acl if it does not exist yet.

snippets.title: ManagedKafka removeAclEntry Sample
snippets.description: Incremental update: Removes an acl entry from an acl. Deletes the acl if its acl entries become empty (i.e. if the removed entry was the last one in the acl).
